com.amaxilatis.ehr.exception

Class EhrClientException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • com.amaxilatis.ehr.exception.EhrClientException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class EhrClientException
extends RuntimeException
    An Exception that occurred during an EhrClient method invocation. This Exception will always include the status code and status message of the request that failed.
    Author:
    Dimitris Zarras
